'''Tasusit''' neɣ '''Tacelḥit''' (s [[tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]]: ⵜⴰⵙⵓⵙⵉⵜ, ⵜⴰⵛⵍⵃⵉⵜ) d [[tutlayt]] i ttmeslayen [[Icelḥiyen|isusiyen]] deg tmurt n [[Ameṛṛuk|umeṛṛuk]], Tasusit d yiwet seg [[tutlayin timaziɣin]], dɣa tettas-d d nettat i d tamezwarut si tama n wemḍan n yemdanen i yettmeslayen s yis, anda amḍan n yimsawalen-is yewweṭ ahat 12 imelyan, syin teṭṭafar-itt-id [[Taqbaylit|Teqbaylit]] s wazal n 7 n imelyan. Ma ɣas tutlayt [[tamaziɣt]] zik tettwaru s isekkilen n [[tifinaɣ|tfinaɣ]], ila tura mas titaran s isekkilen ilatiniyen neɣ s isekkilen aɛraben, maca iseggasen-a igguran yelesd [[IRCAM]] iseffeɣ-d yiwen n ugemmay amahnu f [[tifinaɣ]] tamzikt. Imyura i d-yessufuɣen idlisen, nutni deg tuget deg-sen ttarun s isekkilen ilatiniyen n temɛemmrit.

Ɣas akken ula d tasusit kecmen-tt wawalen n [[taɛrabt]], nezmer ad d-nini d akken d nettat yakk i d [[tantala]] ideg ttugẓen (ttuḥerzen) waṭas n wawalen imaziɣen iẓaranen seld n [[tutlayin titergiyin|Tetergit]],  amedya d izwilen (chiffres) i d-mazal deg-s ar assa, ayen yeǧǧan [[Iqbayliyen]] i d-yelhan d usegmi n tutlayt-nsen d usekfel n tgemmi tutlayant tamzikt ad d-agmen aṭas seg-s aladɣa seg iseggasen-nni n 70 ɣer da.

Tella tattayt n [[:shi:Tasna_n_usnubg|Wikipedia s tcelḥiyt]].

